</section>

<div class="divider-wrap"><div class="divider"></div></div>

<section class="reasons">

  <div class="reason-card">
    <span class="reason-number">01</span>
    <span class="reason-tag">服務熱忱</span>
    <h2>幫助每一位走進門的客人</h2>
    <p class="zh">
      我很期待能夠去幫助那些需要幫助的客人，比方說教他們如何設定基本設置、協助轉到其他地區下載特定的應用程序，以及介紹蘋果的造圖 AI 技術等等 <span class="emoji-accent">✨</span>。我也希望讓那些只是進來逛逛的客人，同樣能感受到蘋果大家庭 <span class="emoji-accent">🏠</span> 的和諧與友善，平等地對待每一位走進來的客人。
    </p>
    <div class="en-block">
      <p class="en-label">English</p>
      <p class="en">
        I am looking forward to helping guests who need assistance — teaching them how to configure basic settings, helping them switch regions to download specific apps, and introducing Apple's AI image-generation capabilities. I also want those who simply drop in to browse to feel the warmth and harmony of the Apple family, and to treat every single visitor with equal care and respect.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="reason-card">
    <span class="reason-number">02</span>
    <span class="reason-tag">自我實現</span>
    <h2>讓興趣與職業相交的機會</h2>
    <p class="zh">
      這個工作機會對我而言，是對於自我實現的滿足。我希望未來的職業能與我的興趣愛好有所連結，這樣才能在工作中更有活力，並保持積極的工作態度。比起推銷名牌包包 <span class="emoji-accent">👜</span> 或沖一杯咖啡 <span class="emoji-accent">☕</span>，我更喜愛科技產品，所以我下定決心投遞履歷給貴公司，期盼能有機會成為蘋果的一份子。
    </p>
    <div class="en-block">
      <p class="en-label">English</p>
      <p class="en">
        This opportunity represents a genuine path to self-fulfillment for me. I believe a career connected to one's passions brings sustained energy and a positive work attitude. I prefer technology products to selling designer bags or brewing coffee, which is exactly why I made the determined decision to submit my résumé to Apple. I hope to have the chance to become part of this extraordinary family.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<footer>
  <p>Crafted with care · 用心製作 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Apple Application Letter</p>
</footer>

